Nathan, the videos are very easy to locate as Juli stated.  You can even go to ufogeek.com to see the videos.  It&#39;s a very simple procedure. 

As far as your personal beliefs go, that&#39;s your choice and I have no problem with that.  However, it&#39;s important to be respectful of the others here who may not share in these same beliefs. 

If the concerns you posted are very real to you, perhaps you should think twice about doing this research.  That&#39;s my opinion.

Jeremy


